  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cancer is second leading cause of death worldwide. The psychological issues are related to
      all stages of the disease affecting outcome of treatment and overall quality of life. The
      study evaluated the effectiveness of yoga counselling among prostate cancer patients on their
      quality of life and psychological outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
